nodes.text: "Green Five" was a human male pilot that served in the early rebellion during the early rebellion against the Galactic Empire. Around 2 BBY, he served as Green Five of Green Squadron, where he flew an A-wing and was tasked with escorting a GR-75 medium transport near Teralov along with 5 other A-wings. The convoy came under attack by Imperials and all rebel ships were destroyed by the TIE/IN interceptors.
This pilot wore a red flight suit and a white helmet with a red and orange markings. He flew an A-wing, that was light grey and green.
The character first appeared in the Star Wars Rebels "The Antilles Extraction", where his voice was provided by Dave Filoni .
